International Journal of Research science and Management

[IJRSMCallforpaper Volume6 Issue 10, October-2019 issue]

International journal of Research science and Management-IJRSMwelcomes the original research article, reviewpapersand shortpapersfor the issue ofAugust 2019. Manuscripts submitted to this journal will be deemed as they have not been published and are not under consideration for publication elsewhere.

Submit your article:editorijrsm@gmail.com mailto:editorijrsm@gmail.comor

Click to submit online:http://ijrsm.com/submit_manuscript_online.php http://ijrsm.com/submit_manuscript_online.php

Submit yourpaperin the form of Mircrosoft word format ( .doc or .docx ) , if you were used latex then send it PDF format.

Click here to download theCopyrights form http://www.ijrsm.com/issues%20pdf%20file/IJRSM_copyright.pdfandPaperTemplate http://www.ijrsm.com/issues%20pdf%20file/IJRSM_Manuscript.docx

