15thOctober 2019

Publication Date

28thOctober2019

Publication Charges

Indian Author(s)Rs 1500/- upto 3 authors, after 3 authors charges will be Rs 500/author Rs 300/author for Hard copy of certificate.Foreign Author(s)$ 80 USD upto 6 AuthorsPapersare published upon acceptance, regardless of the Regular Issue publication date.

